title: Tunisia: President of Republic Inaugurates Frigate Made in Tunisia 'Al Istiqlal'
text:
Tunisia: Bank Recapitalisation Bill Passed 
A presentation was given on the shipbuilding sector in Tunisia and its contribution to boosting the national economy. 
The "Al-Istiqlal" frigate was constructed by Tunisian experts as part of partnership between the public and private sectors. 
The frigate, the studies for its implementation began in 2012, meets international standards. It is equipped with a comprehensive monitoring system and has high propulsive force. 
The new frigate, whose cost is 40% lower than international market prices, provides great support to the national fleet in border control of sea areas. Tunisia
